      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] She used to sing a song [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] [YIDDISH], which means on his lap.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The words rhyme in the--",
